Tree species counts in Pennsylvania survey sites

Source: R/datasets.R
species_occs.Rd

This dataset contains trees species counts in sites sampled in Pennsylvania. This dataset shows the format of the argument site_species used in several functions of funbiogeo. Note that sites labels are specified in row names.

species_occs

Format

A matrix with 5,770 rows (sites) and 93 columns (species).

Examples

data("species_occs")
class(species_occs)

#> [1] "matrix" "array" 
dim(species_occs)

#> [1] 5770   93
